emuInput.TitMainTitle: Urban League Card-O-Rama planning members seated from left: Barbara Davis, Geraldine Goode; standing: Agnes Jones, Ardelle Douglas, and Lillian Haley posed behind table in interior with circular patterned curtains
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper January 9, 1960, pg. 20, reads: "Card-O-Rama Committee - Planning the card party, which will be given Jan. 15, 8 P.M., at the Homewood-Brushton YWCA, Kelly St., by the Upland Young Adult Unit of the Urban League, the committee makes final notations on its affair. Featured will be beautiful prizes, refreshments and a bonus for those arriving on time. Tickets may be secured from Barbara Davis, FR. 1-8015; Ardelle Douglas, PE. 1-1394, or any unit member. Pictured are Agnes Jones, Ardelle Douglas, chairman; Lillian Haley. Seated: Barbara Davis, president, and Geraldine Goode. - Harris Photo."
